the object store to scale out much more easily than a traditional shared file
system.&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>What is a Group Workspace?</title><link>https://mjpritchard.github.io/test-decap-help/docs/short-term-project-storage/introduction-to-group-workspaces/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://mjpritchard.github.io/test-decap-help/docs/short-term-project-storage/introduction-to-group-workspaces/</guid><description>&lt;h2 id="introduction" class="heading">Introduction&lt;a href="#introduction" aria-labelledby="introduction">
